data.description: Welcome to this charming brick ranch nestled in the sought-after area of Canton. Boasting 1,523 square feet of comfortable living space, this meticulously maintained home offers the perfect blend of classic charm and modern updates. Built in 1956 on a spacious 0.47-acre lot, this property features three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms. As you step inside, notice the warmth and character of the home, highlighted by the inviting living areas and abundant natural light. The fenced-in backyard provides a private outdoor space perfect for entertaining or gardening The .47-acre lot offers plenty of room for outdoor activities and expansion possibilities. Partial basement, providing additional storage space and potential for customization to suit your needs. Desirable location, spacious layout, this brick ranch in Canton offers a wonderful opportunity to experience comfortable and convenient living in a highly sought-after area. Don't miss your chance to make this your dream home!
